'''窝尼语'''(自称: ''{{IPA|hɑ31 ɲi33}}'')<ref name="Yang2016"/>是一种在中国[[云南省|云南省]][[镇沅彝族哈尼族拉祜族自治县|镇沅彝族哈尼族拉祜族自治县]]和[[新平彝族傣族自治县|新平彝族傣族自治县]]使用的[[哈尼语|南部]][[彝语支|彝语支]]语言。对窝尼语最详尽的记录是Yang (2016)。<ref name="Yang2016">杨艳. 2016. ''哈尼语窝尼话研究''. Ph.D. dissertation, 上海师范大学.</ref>

有5,406名窝尼语使用者在云南中南部。<ref name="Yang2016"/> 杨艳(2016)记载了新平县勒达村窝尼方言<ref name="ynszxc.net">{{Cite web | url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=250749 |title = 新平县桂山镇亚尼村民委员会二组（勒达）}}</ref>高华年(1955)<ref>高华年. 1955. ''揚武哈尼語初探''. [中山大学学报:社会科学]. 1955, Vol. 2.</ref>和新平县扬武镇方言。

==分类==
杨艳(2016)将窝尼语归为[[豪尼语|豪白方言]]。

==分布==
窝尼语主要分布在下列村(杨艳2016:1-2)。

*[[峨山彝族自治县|峨山彝族自治县]]
**[[岔河乡|岔河乡]]: 回龙村、青龙寨、<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249765 |title = 峨山县岔河乡青河村民委员会青龙寨村}}</ref>哈龙,<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249768 |title = 峨山县岔河乡青河村民委员会哈龙村}}</ref>布度冲、<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249766 |title = 峨山县岔河乡青河村民委员会布渡冲村}}</ref>三家人、<ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249721</ref>新寨、<ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249722</ref>旧寨、<ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249723</ref>乌木村、<ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249728</ref><ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249727</ref>谢家村、<ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249729</ref><ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249730</ref>棚祖坝、<ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249724</ref><ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249731</ref>梁家村、<ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249720</ref>等
**[[化念镇|化念镇]]: 罗里河、<ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249838</ref>羊毛冲、<ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249843</ref>老行寨、<ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249861</ref>马鹿塘、<ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249860</ref>他达莫、<ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249862</ref>法图山、<ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=249841</ref>等
*[[新平彝族傣族自治县|新平彝族傣族自治县]]
**亚尼社区: 勒达小组<ref name="ynszxc.net"/>和岔河小组<ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=250748</ref>
**[[扬武镇|扬武镇]]: 居拉里村<ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=251695</ref><ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=251698</ref>(来自峨山县马鹿塘和老行寨)(语言现已灭亡<ref name="Bradley2001">Bradley, David. 2001. ''Northern Hani dialects''. Paper presented at ICSTLL 34, Kunming, China, 24–28 October 2001.</ref>)
*[[晋宁县|晋宁县]]: [[夕阳彝族乡|夕阳彝族乡]](在6个村)
*[[石屏县|石屏县]]: [[龙武镇|龙武镇]](在育英村<ref>http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=129674</ref>)

另一十分相似的语言变体在[[通海县|通海县]](''通海县志'' 1992:611-612):
*团田村: 梅子箐, 马尾寨和独家村
*水塘村: 新寨

